our boggle game has some features that make the game clear and understandable.

1.first there is an instructions button that describes the rules of the game so the player will know for what words
he can get score for and what is count as a valid word.

2.there is a scrollbar for the list box that allowed the player to see what words did he already found and
its presents it in clean and readable way.

3.if the player taps on the reset button by accident it raises a pop up message to him and ensure that the player 
wants to start over or does he wants to keep with the current game.

4.at the end of the game there is a pop up message asking the player if he wants to start a new game or wants to 
leave. in case he choose to play again the game is reset and otherwise the game is close.

  

